      • generateReports

        public static java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> generateReports()
        1st Lambda function within generate reports method: apps.compute This lambda in combination with the hashmap allows easier assignment of appointmets based on month and quick access when generating reports. 2nd lambda function: contactApps lambda this lambda function uses a comparator to sort the appointments which are already grouped by contact id in chronological order. allows quick access and makes code easy to understand.
